snippet.title: American Gladiators (SNES) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A playthrough of Gametek's 1993 Super NES TV show adaptation, American Gladiators.

It looks reasonably good, and the one (!) song is pretty sweet, but where's the crazy screaming noises? I'll take the NES version over this any day. 

Once you figure out the timing and the angles on the events, they're pretty much no brainers. :/ Oh, and I guess the big digitzed photos are pretty cool. 
_____
No cheats were used during the recording of this video.
